<ul>
<li><a href="/wiki/H2G2" title="H2G2" class="mw-redirect">h2g2</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/Towel_Day" title="Towel Day">Towel Day</a></li>
<li><a href="/wiki/The_Hitchhiker%27s_Guide_to_the_Future" title="The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Future">The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Future</a>, Adams' final project for <a href="/wiki/BBC_Radio_4" title="BBC Radio 4">BBC Radio 4</a> before his death.</li>
<li><a href="/wiki/42_puzzle" title="42 puzzle" class="mw-redirect">42 puzzle</a>, the 42 Puzzle is a game devised by Douglas Adams in 1994 for the United States series of <i>The Hitchhiker's Guide to the Galaxy</i> books.</li>
</ul>
